1. *Robert* je došao u školu ranije danas. (Robert came to school earlier today.)
2. On je poznat kao *Robert* u našem gradu. (He is known as Robert in our town.)
3. *Robert* je izabran za predsednika. (Robert was elected president.)
4. *Roberte*, dođi i pomozi nam! (Robert, come and help us!)
5. *Robertov* sin je takođe veoma uspešan. (Robert's son is also very successful.)
6. Ona je puno putovala sa *Robertom*. (She travelled a lot with Robert.)
7. *Robertu* je bilo potrebno da se prilagodi novim uslovima. (Robert had to adapt to the new conditions.)
8. Svi smo se trudili da zadovoljimo zahteve *Roberta*. (We all tried to meet Robert's requirements.)